# OpenVera

*Vague idea → researched → shipped → remembered*

**Start here.** This is the top-level workspace. The harness lives in `vera-system/`.

## Boot

Read `vera-system/CLAUDE.md` now and follow its boot sequence.

## Layout

```
vera/                    ← you are here (Claude Code opens this)
├── vera-system/         ← the harness (brain, skills, memory, patterns)
└── vera-projects/       ← your work output (projects, research, plans)
```

All harness files are in `vera-system/`. All output goes to `vera-projects/`. Never mix them.

